flowchart LR
 A[Admin / Receptionist] --> S[Patient Servlet] --> V[PatientService]
 V --> P[PatientDao] --> O[(Oracle)]
 V --> U[UserDao] --> O
 V --> R[RoleDao] --> O
 C1[Create without login] --> P
 C2[Create with login] --> T[USERS + PATIENTS transaction] --> V
 E[Update] --> V
 D[Deactivate] --> B{Future appointment or ADMITTED?}
 B -->|Yes| X[Blocked + audit]
 B -->|No| I[PATIENTS + USERS inactive transaction]
